28
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:34,340
SPEAKER_19: Why don't you have a go?
Show them what it takes.

124
00:13:45,279 --> 00:13:48,149
SPEAKER_19: It's all in order, I'll be going.

125
00:13:49,919 --> 00:13:54,379
SPEAKER_19: Master Fugui, don't think badly of me...

126
00:13:54,860 --> 00:13:56,950
SPEAKER_19: for leaving you homeless.

127
00:13:57,960 --> 00:14:00,590
SPEAKER_19: But I sure like that mansion of yours.

128
00:14:00,899 --> 00:14:03,230
SPEAKER_19: See you there in a few days.

131
00:14:10,409 --> 00:14:12,710
SPEAKER_19: Master Fugui, I'm sorry...

132
00:14:12,779 --> 00:14:15,769
SPEAKER_19: but you've nothing left.
What would you wager?

133
00:14:16,110 --> 00:14:18,809
SPEAKER_19: If you're unhappy, talk to Mr. Xie.

188
00:19:58,690 --> 00:20:00,920
SPEAKER_19: Until you're set up elsewhere.

226
00:24:04,400 --> 00:24:07,099
SPEAKER_19: Master Fugui! It's been a year at least.

228
00:24:09,470 --> 00:24:11,769
SPEAKER_19: This old home of yours is great.

229
00:24:12,180 --> 00:24:14,369
SPEAKER_19: Warm in winter, cool in summer.

230
00:24:14,440 --> 00:24:16,470
SPEAKER_19: Great at any price.

231
00:24:19,420 --> 00:24:22,009
SPEAKER_19: I've given up the puppet troupe.

232
00:24:22,119 --> 00:24:23,519
SPEAKER_19: Have a seat.

233
00:24:25,619 --> 00:24:28,990
SPEAKER_19: I don't gamble anymore.
Don't want to end up like you.

240
00:24:53,549 --> 00:24:56,710
SPEAKER_19: I'm not one to lend money.

241
00:24:58,190 --> 00:25:03,150
SPEAKER_19: I'll lend you something else. More practical.

242
00:25:10,829 --> 00:25:13,930
SPEAKER_19: I never had to beg
when I ran the puppet troupe.

243
00:25:14,200 --> 00:25:16,190
SPEAKER_19: Earn your money yourself.

244
00:25:17,539 --> 00:25:19,529
SPEAKER_19: Put together a troupe.

343
00:42:59,670 --> 00:43:01,190
SPEAKER_19: It's your daddy.

344
00:43:06,980 --> 00:43:08,440
SPEAKER_19: What are you doing?

345
00:43:10,280 --> 00:43:11,769
SPEAKER_19: Where's mommy?

485
00:56:50,159 --> 00:56:51,530
SPEAKER_19: Enough?

486
00:56:51,699 --> 00:56:54,690
SPEAKER_19: Still not enough? Okay, I'll fill it right up.

487
00:56:56,039 --> 00:56:58,269
SPEAKER_19: Big ambition for a little kid.

488
00:56:59,570 --> 00:57:01,539
SPEAKER_19: It's more than enough.

489
00:57:01,840 --> 00:57:04,570
SPEAKER_19: So gobble away. Help yourself to sauces.

490
00:57:10,480 --> 00:57:13,010
SPEAKER_19: Youqing, I'll help you stir that up.

491
00:57:14,019 --> 00:57:15,820
SPEAKER_19: What a big appetite!

492
00:57:17,360 --> 00:57:19,329
SPEAKER_19: And so much chili sauce!

1085
01:53:49,579 --> 01:53:51,909
SPEAKER_19: I wouldn't dare.

